casebody.data:
Cynthia Walker, D.D.S.
v.
The N.C. State Board of Dental Examiners No. 95PA16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016 Mr. Ryan McKaig, Ms. Elizabeth Brooks Scherer, Attorneys at Law, For Walker, Cynthia (D.D.S.) Ms. Carolin Bakewell, Attorney at Law, For The N.C. State Board Of Dental Examiners

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 18th of March 2016 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."

Therefore the case is docketed as of the date of this order's certification. Briefs of the respective parties shall be submitted to this Court within the times allowed and in the manner provided by Appellate Rule 15(g)(2).

WITNESS my hand and the seal of the Supreme Court of North Carolina, this the 10th day of June 2016.
